  "description": "Good morning, Fediverse and followers! In case you missed it, I\u0026rsquo;ve finally been getting my website back together - https://emsenn.net\nThere\u0026rsquo;s a lot of slow work to import in old notes, but! I\u0026rsquo;m chugging my way through that, and so should, at some point, be able to start linking to some previously-unpublished essays. (Like one I personally like, that looks at the kids show Phineas and Ferb as a counter-anarcho-nihilism work.) I also have a crapton of tabletop role-playing game source material to upload.\n",
